# Newsletter Includes & Other Info

Shared by newsletter preview and public cruise pages (`newsletter-preview.css`).

## INCLUDES

- White box with **1px `#8DD9BF` border**, 12px radius
- Title **`INCLUDES:`** centred above items (`flex-direction: column`)
- Each item is a **column**: icon above label (not side-by-side)
- No vertical dividers between items
- Icons + labels use dark green **`#245C4E`**
- Items may wrap; do not truncate labels

## OTHER INFO

- Soft mint bar **`#effaf6`**, pill radius (`999px`; stack to `16px` on small screens)
- No grey fill (`#f7f8f8` / `#f4faf7`)
- Label **`OTHER INFO:`** + uppercase message in **`#245C4E`**
- Disclaimer sits immediately under (`margin-top: 8px`)

## Bad

```css
.nl-includes-bar { border-color: #b7d8cc; }
.nl-includes-item { flex-direction: row; border-right: 1px solid #d5e3de; }
.nl-other-info-bar { background: #f7f8f8; }
```

## Good

```css
.nl-includes-bar { border: 1px solid #8DD9BF; background: #fff; flex-direction: column; }
.nl-includes-item { flex-direction: column; align-items: center; color: #245C4E; }
.nl-other-info-bar { background: #effaf6; border-radius: 999px; }
```
